{"tid":53308,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"新手投資求生指南(二)","createTime":"2016-12-24T15:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-09T15:27:56.000Z","uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c1160b9e3fc05a1cfa2d70d06d65a6be54048a2","tid":53308,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:12:33.000Z","msg":"新手投資求生指南<br />\n(一) 投資 儲蓄 平均成本法 EOI<br />\n(二) 平均成本法 讀書方法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一篇文講到 EOI 呢本書推介你用投資成本法買指數基金去達至 market return。然而我對平均成本法是有懷疑的。以下係我對平均成本法買指數的驗証。<br />\n<br />\n我將會計算運用平均成本法每月投入以下三個指數的回報：恆生指數（^HSI），道指（^DJI），以及Nasdaq Composite（^IXIC）。<br />\n<br />\n假設每月在第一個交易日用 $1 以收市價買入指數 I，沒有手續費。指數 I 在第 m 月第一個交易日收市價用 I(m) 來表示。如是者購買十年，便得到：<br />\n<br />\n在第十年基金單位 = 1/I(1) + &hellip; + 1/I(120)<br />\n在第十年基金總值 = 總單位 x I(120)<br />\n<strong>年均平均成本投資增長率 (R_1)</strong> = log(總單位 x I(120) / 120) / 10<br />\n<br />\n我以該十年通帳率作參考：假設第 m 月通帳率為 r(m)<br />\n<strong>年均通帳率 (R_2)</strong> = log((1+r(1)/12)x(1+r(2)/12)x &hellip; x (1+r(120)/12))/10<br />\n<br />\n然後計算 <strong>R_1 - R_2</strong> 得出以下圖表<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/anq8i9x2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fanq8i9x2&h=b5b924e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖表的 x 軸是出售日期，y軸是 R_1 - R_2。例如，倘若你這十年用平均成本法買入HSI，然後今年出售所有 HSI 持貨，不計佣金，相當於平均每年輸通帳 3.4%。又例如，倘若你 98 年買入HSI，然後今年出所有 HSI 持貨，不計佣金，相當於平均每年賺近 10%。<br />\n<br />\n當然，<ins>這並不代表</ins>如果你今天起用平均成本法買入HSI，十年後會相當失望。可是平均成本法的回報，相當取決於指數成份的表現。十年後各個指數會怎樣，我不是先知，我無法預知。在我看來，買了一隻錯誤的基金，無論這隻基金有多分散，最終仍是會叫人失望。<br />\n<br />\n上面的分析，你可能同意，可能不同意。看投資書也應該是這樣。看書必須配合經驗。沒有經驗就必須懷疑。不能盲目信書中所說。因為作者看見的，跟你看見的，未必一樣。他身處的地方，他寫書的年代，也跟你不一樣。不能說，作者所寫的是永恆的真理。只有變幻才是永恆。"},{"pid":"0efb03608d931b78cdb04f440448b563614e8806","tid":53308,"uid":30791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:13:22.000Z","msg":"新手投資求生指南(一)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/46471/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/46471/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"416c97e904898f02be71c907104bcd16dcc5b72b","tid":53308,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:15:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>然後<del>今年</del><span style=\"color: red;\">2008年出售</span>所有 HSI 持貨，不計佣金，相當於平均每年賺近 10%</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b36f070392d915dd07b164e549cd312122c8b82b","tid":53308,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留名"},{"pid":"5cc392a3a237534ba3dc7579ed9e5c54c510e8c6","tid":53308,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:26:11.000Z","msg":"留意錯別字<br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">通脹</span><br />\n唔係通帳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cfa4ebc8fdf30df1d62f320b21047ad82975cdb","tid":53308,"uid":57790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:10:43.000Z","msg":"點解唔一個post講曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ddbfdfd0d79361702f271e6e181644b5b71c618","tid":53308,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:35:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔一個post講曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為好難追 post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f673c685def2ad02316f725118cc743e7f1bc161","tid":53308,"uid":57790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解唔一個post講曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為好難追 post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打繼續出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99713dac6b32e335d9124f6402409103a214578d","tid":53308,"uid":12461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:30:51.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/as